<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Account Deletion Reminder</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
        .countdown {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid #f5576c;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .countdown .days {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #f5576c;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background: #28a745;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background: #218838;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Deletion Reminder</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
        
        <p>This is a reminder that your Pathfinder account is scheduled for permanent deletion.</p>
        
        <div class="countdown">
            <div class="days">{{daysRemaining}}</div>
            <div>days remaining</div>
        </div>
        
        <p>Your account and all associated data will be permanently deleted in <strong>{{daysRemaining}} days</strong>.</p>
        
        <h3>Still want to keep your account?</h3>
        <p>It's not too late! You can cancel the deletion request and keep all your data.</p>
        
        <center>
            <a href="{{cancellationUrl}}" class="button">Cancel Deletion Request</a>
        </center>
        
        <h3>What will be deleted?</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Your profile and account information</li>
            <li>All your experiences and career data</li>
            <li>Your preferences and settings</li>
            <li>Session history and activity logs</li>
            <li>Any custom data you've created</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><strong>Remember:</strong> Once deleted, your data cannot be recovered after 30 days.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated reminder from Pathfinder.</p>
        <p>If you didn't request this deletion, please cancel it immediately.</p>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Pathfinder. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>